Well I recomend READING the ‘Ultimate Server Making Tut’ in the Tut section, but if you have to know.

First, run your Compiler (Hopefully you changed it cuz most ones that come with the source stink)

Secound, Open run server.
Third, open up Moparscape.

fourth. use any Username and Passworld and use the defult Ip (127.0.0.1) and log in.

(If you want your friends to join in they will need Hamachi)
